                            </div>
                            <div class="overflow-hidden">
                                <h5 class="font-weight-normal ls-2 mb-2">Monitor Progress</h5>
                            </div>
                            <div class="overflow-hidden">
                                <p class="font-weight-normal">The Previdence Intelligent Analytics Engine&trade; monitors Key Progress Indicators in an individual's treatment. This allows the organization to know when an individual is or is not responding treatment.  This technology also shows when an individual is not participating in or receiving treatment.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </a>
            </div>
            <!-- / end  service -->
