                                <p class="font-weight-normal">By simplifying and automating compliance, Previdence can help to greatly reduce liability and increase positive treatment outcomes. Through simplifying the processes of compliance to various professional, organizational, state, and federal protocols, procedures, and regulations, Previdence saves time, money, and lives.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </a>
            </div>
            <!-- / end  service -->
        </div>
        <!-- / end  SERVICES LIST -->
